devaru kotta thangi ( kannada : ದೇವರು &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ಟ &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2009 indian kannada film , directed by om sai prakash and produced by smt rajamma &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film stars shiva rajkumar , meera jasmine , monica and suraj in lead roles . the film had musical score by hamsalekha .